This book is intended for technical and non-technical Windows 7 users. This book uses Simple words, Short sentences and Straightforward paragraphs. The triple S and the simplest way of tweaking Windows 7. The topics covered in this book includes an A to Z of proven and tested tips, tricks, tweaks, and hacks for Windows 7 Operating System of Microsoft. This book presents screen shots and step by step discussions of making the performance of Windows 7 better, and some known tricks and tweaks to make the system more efficient. Those familiar with writings about the different hacking, tweaking, and tricks may notice that many of the important ideas, concepts, and principles found in this book came from many authoritative sources with incorporated original ideas of the author.

Windows 7 ABCs: Tips, Tricks, Tweaks, and Hacks Tested For Windows 7 from A-Z
